channel.title: "HighTivity" 317 PKing Server
channel.description:
Hello. I am looking for a partner that can help me code.
I am starting up a server named HighTivity. It'll be a mainly all hybridding server but pure pking and zerker pking is fine aswell. Skilling won't be too important, and maxed cmb stats won't take forever.
I can build a very well website (also graphic design) and I can code pretty well. I just need another coder whos there when I am not.
We can communicate on Skype, MSN, or Ventrilo. I have all of them. I prefer Ventrilo the most.
I have a source/client that we can use. We will be basing it off project insanity.
Message me if interested.
Thank you, anthonyduka
